                            <p>If you’re a people person, have great customer service skills and want to be part of something that affects all of us, then <a href="#0">apply for a job with the census</a>.</p>
                            
                            <p>For Census 2021, we’ll be hiring at least 30,000 field staff across England and Wales. As it gets closer, we’ll be advertising the opportunities online.</p>
                            
